---
import Layout from '../../components/layout/Layout.astro';
import { SITE_NAME, SITE_URL } from '../../config';
import { buildBreadcrumbSchema } from '../../lib/seo';

const title = 'Terms of Use - Service Conditions for Tax Calculators';
const description = 'Terms and conditions for using our Spanish salary and tax calculators. Service nature, intellectual property, privacy, GDPR rights, permitted use and liability limitations.';

const schemas = [
  buildBreadcrumbSchema([
    { name: 'Home', url: '/en/' },
    { name: 'Terms of Use', url: '/en/terms/' },
  ]),
];
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} schema={schemas} locale="en">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-8">
    <nav class="mb-6 text-sm text-medium-gray">
      <a href="/en/" class="hover:text-brand">Home</a> / <span class="text-charcoal dark:text-gray-200">Terms of Use</span>
    </nav>

    <h1 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-bold text-charcoal md:text-4xl dark:text-gray-100">Terms of Use</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-sm max-w-none text-dark-gray dark:text-gray-300 space-y-6">
      <p><em>Last updated: June {new Date().getFullYear()}</em></p>

      <p>
        Welcome to <strong>{SITE_NAME}</strong> ({SITE_URL}). By accessing and using this website, you agree
        to be bound by the following terms and conditions. If you do not agree with any part of these terms,
        please do not use this website. These terms are governed by the General Data Protection Regulation
        (GDPR), the Spanish Organic Law 3/2018 (LOPDGDD), and Law 34/2002 (LSSI-CE).
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal dark:text-gray-100">1. Purpose of the Website</h2>
      <p>
        {SITE_NAME} is an independent information platform providing free online tools for calculating net
        salary, tax withholdings (IRPF), social security contributions, and other financial estimates related
        to Spanish taxation. The website also publishes informational guides about the Spanish tax system.
        All tools and content are provided for informational and educational purposes only and do not
        constitute professional tax, legal, or financial advice.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal dark:text-gray-100">2. Privacy and Data Protection</h2>
      <p>
        All calculations are performed entirely in your browser using client-side JavaScript. No salary data,
        tax class selections, family situation details, or other personal financial information is transmitted
        to our servers. The architecture is designed according to the principle of "privacy by design"
        (Article 25 GDPR). We use Plausible Analytics, a privacy-friendly service that uses no cookies,
        stores no personal data, and is fully GDPR-compliant. See our full
        <a href="/en/privacy-policy/" class="text-brand hover:underline">privacy policy</a> for details.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal dark:text-gray-100">3. Cookies and Local Storage</h2>
      <p>
        This website uses no tracking cookies. No advertising, profiling, or third-party cookies are placed.
        User preferences (such as dark/light mode) are stored in the browser's localStorage, which is not a
        cookie and is never transmitted to our servers. Since no tracking cookies are used, a cookie consent
        banner is not legally required. See our full
        <a href="/en/cookie-policy/" class="text-brand hover:underline">cookie policy</a> for details.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal dark:text-gray-100">4. Accuracy of Calculations</h2>
      <p>
        While we make every effort to ensure the accuracy of our calculators and content based on current
        Spanish legislation, we cannot guarantee that results are error-free or reflect the latest regulatory
        changes. Tax legislation is subject to frequent amendments, and individual circumstances can affect
        actual outcomes. Users should verify calculations with qualified tax advisors or official sources such
        as the Agencia Tributaria (AEAT) before making financial decisions.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal dark:text-gray-100">5. User Responsibilities</h2>
      <p>
        Users agree to use this website in a lawful manner and in accordance with these terms. Users shall
        not: (a) use the website for any illegal or unauthorized purpose; (b) attempt to gain unauthorized
        access to any part of the website, its servers, or any connected systems; (c) reproduce, distribute,
        or modify any content without prior written authorization; or (d) use automated systems to extract
        data from the website (scraping) without express permission.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal dark:text-gray-100">6. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>
        All content, design, code, logos, calculation algorithms, and trademarks on this website are the
        property of Mottalib Radif or its licensors and are protected by Spanish and international
        intellectual property laws. Users may access and use the website for personal, non-commercial purposes
        only. Any other use requires prior written consent. Brief quotations for informational purposes are
        permitted provided the source is credited.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal dark:text-gray-100">7. GDPR Rights</h2>
      <p>
        Under Articles 15 to 22 of the GDPR and the LOPDGDD, you have the right to access, rectify, erase,
        restrict processing, data portability, object to processing, and withdraw consent at any time.
        Since no personal data is collected, these rights are not applicable in practice. You have the right
        to lodge a complaint with the Spanish Data Protection Agency (AEPD) at
        <a href="https://www.aepd.es" class="text-brand hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">www.aepd.es</a>.
        For enquiries, contact us at contacto@elsueldoneto.es.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal dark:text-gray-100">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>
        {SITE_NAME} shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or punitive
        damages arising from the use of or inability to use this website, including but not limited to damages
        resulting from reliance on calculation results or informational content. The website is provided on an
        "as is" and "as available" basis without warranties of any kind, express or implied.
      </p>
      <p>
        The publisher is not responsible for data loss, service interruptions, or damages to user equipment
        resulting from the use of the website.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal dark:text-gray-100">9. External Links</h2>
      <p>
        This website may contain links to third-party websites, including official government sites
        (agenciatributaria.es, seg-social.es). The publisher has no control over the content of these sites
        and disclaims all responsibility for their content, availability, or data protection practices.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal dark:text-gray-100">10. Governing Law</h2>
      <p>
        These terms are governed by and construed in accordance with Spanish law. Any disputes arising from
        the use of this website shall be submitted to the competent courts of Spain, in accordance with
        applicable consumer protection legislation. The potential invalidity of any clause shall not affect
        the remaining provisions.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal dark:text-gray-100">11. Dispute Resolution</h2>
      <p>
        The European Commission provides an online dispute resolution (ODR) platform:
        <a href="https://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr" class="text-brand hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr</a>.
        We are not obliged and not willing to participate in a dispute resolution procedure before a
        consumer arbitration board.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-charcoal dark:text-gray-100">12. Modifications and Contact</h2>
      <p>
        We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time without prior notice. Changes take effect
        immediately upon publication. Continued use of the website after modifications constitutes acceptance
        of the updated terms. For questions, contact us at:<br>
        Email: <a href="mailto:contacto@elsueldoneto.es" class="text-brand hover:underline">contacto@elsueldoneto.es</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
